      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "IRON MIKE TYSON NZ (1) is a newcomer to the Kerryann Morris yard from NZ. He chased star youngster Jumal in his last appearance at Alexandra Park six weeks ago and was progressing strongly prior, winning three of his previous four outings. The ace draw gives him every chance to kick off in Australia with a win. LOCHINVAR JAG (9) had enough speed to lead from the outside barrier before going on to score by 8.5 metres at this circuit and distance last time. Drawn to enjoy a cosy run and if he gets the gaps he may salute again. THE CREEK (3) was a winner here last month and could be close to another success after two successive placings. SPUNKYS GOTSECRETS (4) cannot be left out after solid recent performances, placing from this barrier last week and winning the previous two times he raced here.",
